Description: DroneHone Bluetooth Remote ID sensor bridge for AryaOS
 Exposes Remote ID detections to ATAK DroneHone over Bluetooth Classic
 RFCOMM (external sensor) and optionally BLE OpenDroneID advertisements.
 Ingests DroneScout MQTT and maps to DroneHone JSON wire format.
